
1  

Ido kodol Derube ka Lusitura: nekejai ekesisian ekekiror Timoteo, okoku loka aberu Ayudayat nakiyuunit; konye papake kerai Eyonanit.


2  

Kitejenut iinacan lukiboiete koLusitura ka Ikonium kwape ejokiar ŋesi.


3  Kokotokin Paul ŋol aupakin kaŋes; koyaŋa kokep ŋes kanuka Iyudayan lukejaas atutubeta ŋun, naarai kejenete kere ebe kerai papake Eyonanit. 
4  

Kosodete nakitoritotor oreria, koinakis kes aicorakineta nukicorakinete ikiyakia ka imakio luko Yerusalem tetere ericete. 
5  Kwaŋin kitogogoŋoi ikanisan kotoma aiyuun ŋin, kiyatanakin etiaikec ŋinipaaran.


6  

Kitoroto akwap naka Pirugia ka Galatia, kisimik kes Emoyo Lokalaunan alimonokin akirot toma Asia. 
7  Nakedolioto atereikina Musia, kotama alosit Bitunia, konye mam Emoyo loka Yesu abu kocamak kes, 
8  Aso kinaca Musia kijesaros Tiroa. 
9  Koany Paul aitapoet kuare: bala ebwoi etuŋanan loko Makedonia iŋaiŋait kobala ebe, “Kikwaŋun Makedonia, kiŋarak sio.” 
10  Nakedaunia aanyun aitapoet, atipet kakotos alosit Makedonia, naarai kiwomit cut ebe kinyarit Edeke sio alimonokin kes akiro nukajokak.


11  Aso kekwaŋaros anyoun koTiroa, karasasi Samoturake, kapaaran da naatupakini kadoloto Neapoli. 
12  Kanyoutu kanen kadoloto Pilipi, ere lokapolon loka akwap nako Makedonia, akwap nakebwotunito ice ko Romayon. Keboioto kore kaŋol apaarasia adis. 
13  Kosodi kapaaran nakasabato kalomutu korute kaloto ariri kecor, nekiwomit ebe kejai aibois nakilipet; keboikinos kenerata kaŋor nukidumuni kanen. 
14  

Aberu, ekekiror Ludia, nakegwelanari iboro lumugeik, naka ere loka Tuatira, naeyoŋit Edeke, kopup sio: nakepukorit Ejakait eketau tetere ecoit akiro nuenera Paul. 
15  Kosodi kedau aibatisao, ŋes ka lukokaleke, kiŋaiŋa sio, kobala ebe, “Arai ianyunito eoŋ arai naiyuunit Ejakait, kolomutu togoka kipejoto.” Kitiŋa sio.


16  

Napekilosi aibois naka ailip, keriamata kapese naejai ajokit naka aidwar, nakedumanakini ikejaka ameda naepol naka aidwar. 
17  

Kotupu ŋin Paul ka sio iworoi ebe, “Ituŋa lu eraas ikejaanakinak luka Edeke loejai kuju kakuj, lukilimonokinete yes erot loka aitajario.” 
18  

Kikoni nen apaarasia nuipu. Konye koŋoiar Paul, kibelokin kotema ajokit atiar, “Kecorakini jo kokiror loka Yesu Kristo kolom kamakeŋ.” Kolom kosawa kaŋope kaŋol.


19  Konye nakeanyuniata ijakake ebe atwakiasi ameda naamunos, kikamutu Paul ka Sila, kidilidilasi kiton agwelanaret akonyen nuka ikayaitok; 
20  

koyaŋaasi mama ejaas ikatubok kotemasi atiar, “Ituŋa lu eraas Iyudayan, amunaasi erewok, 
21  bobo da elimonokinete iponesio lueraas luketal kamawok Iromayon acamun karaida aswam.” 
22  

Konyou ekodet kere asurokin kes: kolacasi ikatubok inapenekec kagogoŋ, kicorakis kes aleio kisureta. 
23  Nakedauniata aile noi, kogolokis aidaris, kicorakis ekedaran aidar kes kacoit, 
24  Kedau adumun aicorakinet ŋin, kibwaik kes toma aidaris nakotoma, koen akejekec oloin.


25  Konye kidiŋebai ilipete Paul ka Sila, eyeikinete Edeke ikososio luka aiturit, kopupete ienan da ice; 
26  atipet kojau amaran naepol naka akwap, komaranata apeteta nuka aidaris; atipet koŋaaros ikekia kere, kolacaros da aeneta nuka ituŋa kere, 
27  Kokweny ekedaran, nakeanyunia ebe eŋaara ikekia luka aidaris, kout ekekileŋ, kokoto aarakin, koomit ebe asiata ienan. 
28  Konye kiworo Paul keporoto loepol ebe, “Sirikimusuŋikin, naarai kija isio ne kere.” 
29  Konyarau atalai, komotar toma, emarani kanuka akurian, kibirokin akonyen nuka Paul ka Sila, 
30  

kitolom kiŋa, kotema atiar, “Ikajaka, kekonak ai tetere ketajario?” 
31  Kobalasi ebe, “Kiyuu Ejakait Yesu, kitajario jo ka lukokalekon kere.” 
32  Kolimokis ŋes ka ituŋa kere luajaas togoke akirot naka Ejakait, 
33  Kisukunyik kes kosawa kaŋol loka akuare, kilot ikecemacarin, atipet kibatisai ŋes ka iketuŋa kere. 
34  Kosodi koyau kes togoke, koinak kes inyamat, kolakara noi, ŋes ka ekekale kere, naarai iyuunit Edeke.


35  Konye kiwala akwap, kiyakiasi ikatubok ikapolok luka iserikalei, kobalas ebe, “Koosikis ituŋa ŋul koloto.” 
36  Kitejen ekedaran Paul akiro ŋun ebe, “Eyakuut ikatubok aosikin yes: aso do kolomutu, koloto inapakina.” 
37  

Konye kotema Paul kes atiar, “Apotu koleata sio kakonyen nuka ituŋa kere, komam etubokina, kwabo kirai isio Iromayon, bobo da kigolokis aidaris; kwana da ekotosi cabo alacakin kaiyeiyea? Mam cut; konye kopotu kesi ikulepek kolacakis sio.” 
38  Kolimokis ikapolok luka iserikalei ikatubok akiro ŋun; kokuriakaros nakiirariata ebe eraas ŋul Iromayon; 
39  

kopotu, kiŋaiŋaata; nakedauniata aitolomun, kilipa kes anyoun kore kaŋol. 
40  Konyoutu do kaidaris kolomasi togo loka Ludia: ido kedaut aanyun iinacan, kitalakasi kes, koloto.

